com.toldcalculator.android.tc.model

Class Metar

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.toldcalculator.android.tc.model.Metar

  • public class Metar
extends Object
    This class is used in the deserialization of the xml data received from the FAA Text Data Service. Zero to 1000 metars can be returned in a request. Different elements can be returned based on the station type and current condition. Not all elements available to be returned are in this class at the moment as only a few are needed.
